transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Ji sir. India Mart se baat kar rahi hu Kashish sir kaise hain aap?
Customer: Bas theek hai. Main na aapko lunch ji wo
Executive: Haan ji.
Customer: Haan main aapne jo mujhe wo bheja hai na catalog.
Executive: Haan ji haan ji wo usme karwane the.
Executive: Profile mein add karna hai na.
Customer: Haan wo purane wala hata ke ye wala dal denge.
Executive: Kya sir?
Customer: Purane wala hata ke ye wala lagwa denge.
Executive: Dono mein? Kis kis mein add karna hai? Kar de rahi hu main add iska bata dijiye aap mujhe.
Executive: Jaise ki aapne mujhe do bheje hain Prime Rose launch chair theek hai aur dusra aapne bheja hai Prime Rose form catalog.
Customer: Haan ji haan ji form wala jo hai wo wo pehle hoga wo purane wale ki jagah le lega.
Executive: Theek hai.
Customer: Aur jo ye launch wala hai ye bhi kahin pe agar ho sakta hai ya usi ke sath adjust ho jaye.
Executive: Theek hai sir. Aur sir chair handle category ka na kuch buylead consume karni hai aapko. To ek bar aap dekh lijiyega sir.
Customer: Haan ji.
Customer: Haan main lunch ke baad abhi main office mein nahi hu lunch ke baad main karta hu consume.
Executive: Theek hai. Haan sir main add karti hu profile mein. Okay sir.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai thank you.
